## Step 3: Determine the end value of accounts payable
The end value would be the initial value minus any payments made plus any new accounts payable created during the period.

I don't see any new purchases made on account payable during January 2024, so the end value would be the same as the initial value if no payments were made.

End accounts payable = 5,596,070.00
